Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:10.70,English,,0,0,0,,Inside this box is a really interesting little gadget I want to show you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:14.17,English,,0,0,0,,This is a magnetic tape viewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:18.60,English,,0,0,0,,With this, you can actually see the audio that's recorded on a tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:22.04,English,,0,0,0,,I'll demonstrate how it works with this quarter-inch tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:25.47,English,,0,0,0,,First, I'll layer recorded section of the tape out flat,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:28.23,English,,0,0,0,,and then place the viewer down on top of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:30.87,English,,0,0,0,,Making sure I put it on the recorded side of the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:34.27,English,,0,0,0,,And within a couple of seconds, the pattern of the audio
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:36.74,English,,0,0,0,,that's on the tape appears in the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:40.77,English,,0,0,0,,Now as you could imagine this is not the easiest thing to shoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:43.65,English,,0,0,0,,so I've had to break out the macro lens for this video.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:45.05,English,,0,0,0,,But let's take one more look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:48.12,English,,0,0,0,,So popping it down on the tape, I can determine that
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:50.16,English,,0,0,0,,this is a four track recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:54.77,English,,0,0,0,,I can also see that, it's more than likely to separate stereo programs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:00:59.34,English,,0,0,0,,one going in each direction, as track one matches up with track three,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:01.33,English,,0,0,0,,and track two goes with track four.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:04.85,English,,0,0,0,,Now you might be wondering how much audio in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:08.16,English,,0,0,0,,We're looking at here, how long would it take to play that section of table.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.52,English,,0,0,0,,You probably aren't wondering that but I'm going to tell you anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:14.27,English,,0,0,0,,So this tape is on a seven inch reel, which is a four track.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.89,English,,0,0,0,,So most commonly, recorded at a speed of seven and a half
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:18.95,English,,0,0,0,,or three point seven five inches per second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:21.93,English,,0,0,0,,Or in the case of my reel-to-reel that's listed in metric
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.42,English,,0,0,0,,as 19 or 9.5 cm a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:29.95,English,,0,0,0,,And playing the tape reveals that it's been recorded at that slower speed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:43.86,English,,0,0,0,,So it's a 9.5 cm per second recording.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:47.94,English,,0,0,0,,And the window on the tape viewer is three centimeters across,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:51.96,English,,0,0,0,,which means that that's approximately a third of a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:53.60,English,,0,0,0,,That's visible in the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:56.09,English,,0,0,0,,Now moving on to how it works... 
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:59.46,English,,0,0,0,,Well, it's quite likely a familiar with a toy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:04.18,English,,0,0,0,,The idea being that you use a magnet to manipulate the iron filings
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.87,English,,0,0,0,,that are contained inside the clear plastic window.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:11.78,English,,0,0,0,,Well, imagine if those iron filings were much much finer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:15.29,English,,0,0,0,,and also suspended in a liquid, and then
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.08,English,,0,0,0,,rather than requiring a magnet on a stick to move them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:23.01,English,,0,0,0,,That'd be fine enough to be attracted by the much weaker magnetic signal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.66,English,,0,0,0,,that's recorded on a tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:29.57,English,,0,0,0,,The magnetic attraction of a tape, while weak, is still strong enough to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:31.91,English,,0,0,0,,pass through the thin metal base of the viewer,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:36.10,English,,0,0,0,,and manipulate the ultrafine suspended ferric oxide particles
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.23,English,,0,0,0,,to reveal the recorded pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.89,English,,0,0,0,,Now the earliest mention of seen of this device
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:46.10,English,,0,0,0,,is in this issue of broadcast engineering from February 1964.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.83,English,,0,0,0,,It appears on the new products page for that month.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:52.90,English,,0,0,0,,A number of potential uses are listed, including amongst others.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.58,English,,0,0,0,,Checking for head alignment, track placement and dropouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:03:02.54,English,,0,0,0,,It also says, it can be used to determine if tools tape heads or tape guides are magnetized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:06.86,English,,0,0,0,,The price in 1964 was listed as $50.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:10.57,English,,0,0,0,,With inflation, that's a little over $400 nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.77,English,,0,0,0,,Looking at the patent number that's shown on the viewer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:20.15,English,,0,0,0,,reveals that this was granted in 1961, but it was applied for in 1958.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:24.16,English,,0,0,0,,Originally though, the use case was a little bit less certain in the document.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:27.60,English,,0,0,0,,It states that magnetic recorded tape is often criticzed,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.56,English,,0,0,0,,because the signals are invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:32.72,English,,0,0,0,,It states this as hampered sales due to a reluctance
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.88,English,,0,0,0,,from some organizations to move away from punch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.24,English,,0,0,0,,tape and cards, where the data was visible to the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:40.60,English,,0,0,0,,And therefore, could be verified by a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.60,English,,0,0,0,,The proposed apparatus showed in the documentation
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.52,English,,0,0,0,,is also significantly different in design to the finished product.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:51.78,English,,0,0,0,,Now initially, I wondered if 3M had purchased this patent
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.95,English,,0,0,0,,and adapted that original idea for their viewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:58.20,English,,0,0,0,,But you can see, on the patents, it was three Ms from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:02.79,English,,0,0,0,,Or as it's written in full here: the Minnesota Mining and Manufacturing Company.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.92,English,,0,0,0,,And the primary name that's listed on the application:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:09.80,English,,0,0,0,,Robert J. Youngquist, was a career 3M employee.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:13.77,English,,0,0,0,,He was later inducted into their Carleton Society, which is
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:17.52,English,,0,0,0,,kinda 3M's Hall of Fame, and that was in 1991.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:21.95,English,,0,0,0,,The magnetic tape viewer that here in these colleagues devised 33 years earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.92,English,,0,0,0,,They must have remained on the market for a number of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:28.75,English,,0,0,0,,as it's mentioned again, in this magazine article from 1973.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:31.49,English,,0,0,0,,By this point though, they're suggesting that you could use it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:34.36,English,,0,0,0,,to check the head alignment of an 8-track tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.32,English,,0,0,0,,So let's have a look at one of those!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.43,English,,0,0,0,,Now this one was quite a bit more difficult to get a good picture 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:42.36,English,,0,0,0,,of what issue is that, the tracks are really fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:45.95,English,,0,0,0,,And we're also trying to capture an 0.3 second window,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:50.26,English,,0,0,0,,and all of those eight tracks are playing something loud enough to show up clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:54.21,English,,0,0,0,,But you can just about make out here, all of the eight tracks on this tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.30,English,,0,0,0,,The eight track I'm using is a stereo tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:05:00.02,English,,0,0,0,,so that means it consists of full stereo program.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.09,English,,0,0,0,,So those are made up of pairs of tracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.62,English,,0,0,0,,And they're laid out on the tape as tracks 1 & 5,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:10.10,English,,0,0,0,,2 & 6, 3 & 7, and finally, 4 & 8.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.44,English,,0,0,0,,It's perhaps a little bit easier to see it on this next shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.39,English,,0,0,0,,Where the fourth program is currently silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:22.27,English,,0,0,0,,So that means, we can see for example that tracks 2 & 6 are definitely a matching pair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:27.30,English,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's look at something else. An old store loyalty points card.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.39,English,,0,0,0,,Popping the viewer on here, and you can clearly see the
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.37,English,,0,0,0,,magnetic signal that's recorded on the strip.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.22,English,,0,0,0,,And next, let's move on to a compact cassette.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.02,English,,0,0,0,,Now, this one showed up particularly well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:43.40,English,,0,0,0,,You can clearly see the two stereo programs, one for each side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:49.09,English,,0,0,0,,And this also shows how much of a gap is left, only middle of a compact cassette tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.56,English,,0,0,0,,And there is a real stereo I use the viewer for.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:55.10,English,,0,0,0,,A while ago, I bought this actors master tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:58.83,English,,0,0,0,,It's from a talent agency, it was used to showcase actors voices for 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.01,English,,0,0,0,,potential advertisement jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.75,English,,0,0,0,,Well, from playing it back at my four track machine,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.65,English,,0,0,0,,I could determine the speed of the tape, and also,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:11.75,English,,0,0,0,,I know that it's not a four-track as the recording only plays one way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.12,English,,0,0,0,,But I wasn't sure if any of it was in stereo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:18.32,English,,0,0,0,,Well, to find that out, I can put the view on and putting it down on the tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:20.93,English,,0,0,0,,shows that it's actually a mono recording,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:24.42,English,,0,0,0,,just one track all the way across the width of the tape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.65,English,,0,0,0,,And so, break things up for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.29,English,,0,0,0,,Here's a brief sample of a clip from that reel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.15,English,,0,0,0,,Let's have a look a couple more things through the viewer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:55.92,English,,0,0,0,,This is a two-track stereo tape recorded at 19 centimeters a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.77,English,,0,0,0,,So just like that advert reel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:01.79,English,,0,0,0,,What you're looking at here is approximately one-sixth of a second of audio.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.70,English,,0,0,0,,Now the viewer doesn't work with everything though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.75,English,,0,0,0,,This is what a DCC looks like, which is nothing visible. 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.76,English,,0,0,0,,It's definitely a recorded section of audio, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.90,English,,0,0,0,,It's no surprise it doesn't show up though
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:16.33,English,,0,0,0,,because a DCC has 18 incredibly thin digital tracks across its width.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.36,English,,0,0,0,,It's just going to be too fine for it to register.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.16,English,,0,0,0,,And next is what the recorded section looks like on a VHS tape,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.26,English,,0,0,0,,but the only thing that's visible this time 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.12,English,,0,0,0,,is the controlled track that's a long wad edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.13,English,,0,0,0,,And finally one the church that I wanted to show is that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:34.10,English,,0,0,0,,when the viewer is placed back in its case, it displays the 3M logo.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.97,English,,0,0,0,,Therefore, if you ever do see one of these in a shop, 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:40.20,English,,0,0,0,,you can test whether it's working without having a magnetic tape with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.25,English,,0,0,0,,A word of warning though, the faroe oxide in the fluid
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.44,English,,0,0,0,,can settle to one side over time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.77,English,,0,0,0,,This initially was the case with mine after a couple of minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.52,English,,0,0,0,,So gently massaging the screen in a circular motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.21,English,,0,0,0,,The solution dispersed evenly again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.98,English,,0,0,0,,That said you'd be very lucky to find one of these for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.25,English,,0,0,0,,I had a save search on eBay activated for one of these
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:01.68,English,,0,0,0,,FOR FOUR YEARS before one turned up for sale.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.96,English,,0,0,0,,However, while researching for this video,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.57,English,,0,0,0,,I found that there's a company making a modern-day equivalent
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:09.29,English,,0,0,0,,So if you are interested, I'll put a link to them in
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.74,English,,0,0,0,,the video description text box.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.44,English,,0,0,0,,And I hope you've enjoyed having a look at
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.45,English,,0,0,0,,this fascinating little device here today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.07,English,,0,0,0,,But that is it for the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.16,English,,0,0,0,,As always, thanks for watching.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:10.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,今天我给大家介绍的是这个盒子里的小玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:14.17,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这是个磁带磁性查看器
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.23,0:00:18.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,利用这个，你可以清晰地看到记录在磁带上的音频信号
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.37,0:00:22.04,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我一会用这个四分之一英寸的磁带来演示
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.64,0:00:25.47,Chinese,,0,0,0,,首先，我要将一段录过音的磁带片段抽出来，并铺平
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.49,0:00:28.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后将查看器放在这个上面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.24,0:00:30.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,保证其放在录过音的那一面
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.65,0:00:34.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,几秒后，磁带上音频信号的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.28,0:00:36.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,样子就显示在窗口中了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:40.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当然，正如你能所想，拍下来这个可不是什么容易事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:43.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以我祭出了微距镜头来拍这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:45.05,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在咱来看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.80,0:00:48.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,将其放在磁带上时，我能分辨出
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.13,0:00:50.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个磁带上有四个磁轨
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.17,0:00:54.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且我还注意到，这个好像是将两个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.77,0:00:59.34,Chinese,,0,0,0,,双声道给分开了，比如一磁轨和三磁轨是一对
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:01.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,二磁轨和四磁轨是一对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.79,0:01:04.85,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在你可能在想：这段磁带能放出多长的音频
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.07,0:01:08.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们来看看，这段摆在桌子上的磁带能放多长时间的音频
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.16,0:01:10.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你也许没考虑到，但是我现在还是要说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.12,0:01:14.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，这个磁带是放在七英寸的卷盘上，也就是四轨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:16.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一般来说，这个是以7.5英寸每秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.89,0:01:18.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,或者是3.75英寸每秒的速度录制的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.72,0:01:21.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,要是听不懂的话，我开盘机上显示的是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.93,0:01:25.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,19厘米每秒，或者是9.5厘米每秒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.88,0:01:29.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我在播放磁带后，意识到这盘磁带是以较慢的速度录制的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.86,0:01:43.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，这个就是以9.5厘米每秒的速度录制的了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.86,0:01:47.94,Chinese,,0,0,0,,再来看查看器窗口，这个是三厘米
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:51.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，这段磁带就能播放三分之一秒的音乐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.08,0:01:53.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而这段音乐呢，你就能在查看器窗口里看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.58,0:01:56.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在咱来看看这个的原理......
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.09,0:01:59.46,Chinese,,0,0,0,,额，这个东西的原理和这个玩具的原理差不多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.87,0:02:04.18,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是当你用磁铁来移动铁屑的方向时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.18,0:02:06.87,Chinese,,0,0,0,,铁屑就在这个透明的塑料盒子中移动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.21,0:02:11.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而如果这些铁屑更细
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.78,0:02:15.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且悬浮在液体中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.29,0:02:18.08,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这时，你不必使用磁铁或磁棒来移动它们了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:23.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们足够的细，所以它们可以侦测到更微弱的磁信号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.02,0:02:24.66,Chinese,,0,0,0,,比如磁带上的磁信号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.35,0:02:29.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,磁带上的磁信号，虽然很弱，但是也足以
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:31.91,Chinese,,0,0,0,,能穿过查看器底部的金属片了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.91,0:02:36.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,然后让其上的十分细的悬浮氧化铁粒子移动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.23,Chinese,,0,0,0,,来显示出磁带上的磁信号
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.95,0:02:40.89,Chinese,,0,0,0,,目前关于这个东西的最早记载
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:46.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,是在1964年2月的出版的《Broadcast Engineering》杂志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:46.10,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：参考译名《广播工程》
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它是出现在“本月新上市产品”栏目中的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.42,0:02:52.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还列出了很多潜在用途，包括其他方面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.58,Chinese,,0,0,0,,例如检查磁头是否校准，查看磁轨位置和边缘
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:03:02.53,Comments,,0,0,0,,注：这些开盘带之类的术语我全都不知道是什么意思，有谁懂的话，发下弹幕补充一下呗:-)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.59,0:03:02.54,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这上面还说，这个东西还能侦测到磁头，磁带导引器这些东西是否被磁化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.65,0:03:06.86,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个玩意1964年时卖50美元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.87,0:03:10.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,算上通货膨胀的话，现在卖400多美元
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.19,0:03:13.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,再来看看查看器上面印的专利号
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.77,0:03:20.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,显示是在1961年授予的，问题是，他们早在1958年就申请了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.74,0:03:24.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,原先的申请档案中，这个发明的目的没写清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:27.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这上面说：录音磁带广受差评
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:29.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为录上去的信号看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.56,0:03:32.72,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这上面还说：这个特性导致磁带销售缓慢，因为
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.73,0:03:34.88,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为有些机构不愿将打孔带替下来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:38.24,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为打孔带上可以看见数据:-|
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:40.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,从而，这个人就可以辨别信息了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.07,0:03:43.60,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而且，这个文档中正在设计的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.60,0:03:47.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,和我手中的最终成品还是有所差异的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.23,0:03:51.78,Chinese,,0,0,0,,原先呢，我想3M是不是买进这个专利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:54.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并采纳了这个查看器的设计思路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:58.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是如你所见，在专利文件开头有三个M
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.20,0:04:02.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有这个全称：明尼苏达矿业及机器制造公司
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.41,0:04:05.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有这份申请中的第一个申请人：
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:09.80,Chinese,,0,0,0,,Robert J. Youngquist，当时是3M的员工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.34,0:04:13.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它后来被引进3M的Carleton Society
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.78,0:04:17.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个相当于3M的名人堂，他是在1991年被引入的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.08,0:04:21.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而他们是在33年前设计的磁带磁性查看器
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.96,0:04:24.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些东西大概在市场上售卖了几年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.93,0:04:28.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,正如1973年发行的杂志上的文章所言
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.15,0:04:31.49,Chinese,,0,0,0,,说到这个，他们建议你用这个来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:34.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,检测八轨磁带头是否对齐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.37,0:04:36.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，咱来试试这个
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.93,0:04:39.43,Chinese,,0,0,0,,额，要把这个拍下来还是有一定难度的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.43,0:04:42.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,问题在于，磁轨太细了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.37,0:04:45.95,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我们仍然尝试拍下有0.3秒音频磁带的磁性分布
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.95,0:04:50.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,而这段磁带的八个轨道，信号都很强，能够让我们很清晰地看见它们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:54.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你现在就能辨别出这个磁带上的八个轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.98,0:04:57.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这盘八轨带是双声道的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.30,0:05:00.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是整盘带都是双声道信号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是说，这些轨道都是成对的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.39,0:05:05.62,Chinese,,0,0,0,,它们在磁带上是以1和5
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.62,0:05:10.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,2和6，3和7，以及4和8的方式配对的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.94,0:05:13.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也许在下一张图片中，我们可以看得更清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:16.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,目前磁带上的第四轨道是没有音频信号的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:22.27,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是说，我们可以分明地看见这些轨道的配对关系，比如2轨和6轨
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:27.30,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，咱现在来看点别的。一张十分老的商店会员积分卡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.76,0:05:30.39,Chinese,,0,0,0,,咱现在把查看器放在上面，然后你就能看到
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.39,0:05:33.37,Chinese,,0,0,0,,记在磁条上面的磁信号
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:36.22,Chinese,,0,0,0,,现在，我们再来看看稀松平常的盒式磁带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.02,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个磁带在显示器中显示得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:43.40,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你可以分明地看到两个双声道信号，一边一个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.73,0:05:49.09,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你也可以看到这两个轨道间的空隙有多窄，就是磁带中间的一小段
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.11,0:05:52.56,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这里我们还要用查看器来看看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:55.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,很久之前，我买了这盘播音员试音带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.11,0:05:58.83,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这原先是经纪公司做的，用来展现播音员的声色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.83,0:06:01.01,Chinese,,0,0,0,,用来看他们适不适合给广告配音
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我把这盘带放在开盘机上播放后
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.76,0:06:06.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我可以确定磁带录制的速度，而且
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.65,0:06:11.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我还知道这不是四轨磁带，而且只能朝一个方向播放
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:15.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是我不知道这盘磁带是不是双声道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.13,0:06:18.32,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好吧，为了看出这个，我把查看器放在磁带的上面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:20.93,Chinese,,0,0,0,,看出这个就是单声道的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.93,0:06:24.42,Chinese,,0,0,0,,整条磁带只有这一条单声道音轨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:26.65,Chinese,,0,0,0,,那么，咱截下来一段来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.81,0:06:29.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,以下是这盘磁带的片段
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.15,Chinese,,0,0,0,,咱们现在用这个查看器再来看点别的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:55.92,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个是双轨的磁带，录制速度为19厘米每秒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以这个和刚才的广告试音带没什么区别
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:07:01.79,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你现在所看到的是大约六分之一的声音信号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:03.70,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但这个查看器不能看到所有的磁信号:-(
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.75,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个是DCC在查看器中看到的效果，啥都看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.71,0:07:06.75,Comments,,0,0,0,,注: {\fnComic Sans MS\fs55}DCC=Digital Compact Cassette {\fn文泉驿等宽微米黑\fs50}数字式高密录音带
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:09.76,Chinese,,0,0,0,,可这段绝对是录上音的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.02,0:07:11.90,Chinese,,0,0,0,,额，它显示不出来是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:16.33,Chinese,,0,0,0,,因为DCC磁带上有18个十分细的数码轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.36,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这些轨道十分的细，难以被侦测到
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,下一个实验对象是VHS磁带
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.17,0:07:24.26,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是你只能看到边缘的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.27,0:07:27.12,Chinese,,0,0,0,,控制信号轨道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:30.13,Chinese,,0,0,0,,好的，最后一个我想展示的是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.14,0:07:34.10,Chinese,,0,0,0,,当你把查看器放回盒子中时，你会看到3M的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.97,Chinese,,0,0,0,,也就是说，当你在商场看到他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.98,0:07:40.20,Chinese,,0,0,0,,你不必带一段磁带来检测这个东西能不能用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.21,0:07:43.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有个问题需要注意，这个东西放久的话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.45,0:07:45.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,流体中的氧化铁会聚集到一侧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.77,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一开始我以为是我没用好，过了几分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.78,0:07:50.52,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我轻轻地打转查看器才解决了这个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.16,0:07:53.21,Chinese,,0,0,0,,这个问题时常还会出现:-(
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.98,Chinese,,0,0,0,,还有一件事，你要能找到的话，你就太幸运了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.17,0:07:59.25,Chinese,,0,0,0,,在我买到这个东西前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.26,0:08:01.68,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我已经花了四年时间在eBay上寻找这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.18,0:08:03.96,Chinese,,0,0,0,,但是呢，我在查资料时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:06.57,Chinese,,0,0,0,,我看到有家公司在做这个设备
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.58,0:08:09.29,Chinese,,0,0,0,,所以，如果你感兴趣的话，我会将这个公司的连接
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.74,Chinese,,0,0,0,,放在简介区里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.07,0:08:12.44,Chinese,,0,0,0,,希望大家对今天我展示的小东西感兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:14.45,Chinese,,0,0,0,,并且看得愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:16.07,Chinese,,0,0,0,,不过，本期节目到此就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.27,0:08:18.16,Chinese,,0,0,0,,一如既往，感谢大家观看:-)
